headline: T. ROWE PRICE GROUP REPORTS PRELIMINARY MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT FOR JUNE 2025
summary: T. Rowe Price Group, Inc. (NASDAQ-GS: TROW) announced preliminary month-end assets under management of $1.68 trillion as of June 30, 2025. Preliminary net outflows in June 2025 were $7.0 billion, primarily driven by the timing of a few redemptions and client rebalancing. For the quarter-ended June 2025, net outflows were $14.9 billion, including $0.7 billion of manager-driven distributions.
